es, so it blows scorching flames to make the environment suit\u00ad able for itself."},{"version":"silver","text":"The fiery surface of its body gives off a wavering, rippling glare that is similar to the sun."},{"version":"crystal","text":"It moves more frequently in hot areas. It can heal itself by dipping its wound into lava."},{"version":"ruby","text":"In battle, MAGMAR blows out intensely hot flames from all over its body to intimidate its opponent. This POK\u00e9MON\u2019s fiery bursts create heat waves that ignite grass and trees in its surroundings."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"In battle, MAGMAR blows out intensely hot flames from all over its body to intimidate its opponent. This POK\u00e9MON\u2019s fiery bursts create heat waves that ignite grass and trees in its surroundings."},{"version":"emerald","text":"In battle, it blows out intense flames from all over its body to intimidate its foe. These fiery bursts create heat waves that ignite grass and trees in the area."},{"version":"firered","text":"Found near the mouth of a volcano. This fire-breather\u2019s body temperature is nearly 2,200 degrees Fahrenheit."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Its body always burns with an orange glow that enables it to hide perfectly amidst flames."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Born in the spout of a volcano, its body is covered by flames that shimmer like the sun."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Born in the spout of a volcano, its body is covered by flames that shimmer like the sun."},{"version":"platinum","text":"When it breathes deeply, heat waves form around its body, making it hard to see clearly."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It dislikes cold places, so it blows scorching flames to make the environment suitable for itself."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"The fiery surface of its body gives off a wavering, rippling glare that is similar to the sun."},{"version":"black","text":"When it breathes deeply, heat waves form around its body, making it hard to see clearly."},{"version":"white","text":"When it breathes deeply, heat waves form around its body, making it hard to see clearly."},{"version":"black-2","text":"The scorching fire exhaled by Magmar forms heat waves around its body, making it hard to see the Pok\u00e9mon clearly."},{"version":"white-2","text":"The scorching fire exhaled by Magmar forms heat waves around its body, making it hard to see the Pok\u00e9mon clearly."},{"version":"x","text":"Found near the mouth of a volcano. This fire-breather\u2019s body temperature is nearly 2,200 degrees Fahrenheit."},{"version":"y","text":"Born in the spout of a volcano, its body is covered by flames that shimmer like the sun."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"In battle, Magmar blows out intensely hot flames from all over its body to intimidate its opponent. This Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s fiery bursts create heat waves that ignite grass and trees in its surroundings."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"In battle, Magmar blows out intensely hot flames from all over its body to intimidate its opponent. This Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s fiery bursts create heat waves that ignite grass and trees in its surroundings."},{"version":"sun","text":"When it\u2019s tired, it leaps into the mouth of a volcano and soaks its body in magma to ease its weariness. Its body burns at 2,192 degrees F."},{"version":"moon","text":"When angered, it spouts brilliant fire from all over its body. It doesn\u2019t calm down until its opponent has burned to ash."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Its entire body is burning. When it breathes, the temperature rises. When it sneezes, flames shoot out!"},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"The hotter the place, the better they feel. Magmar in Alola are said to be hardier than those in other areas."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Born in an active volcano. Its body is always cloaked in flames, so it looks like a big ball of fire."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Born in an active volcano. Its body is always cloaked in flames, so it looks like a big ball of fire."},{"version":"sword","text":"Magmar dispatches its prey with fire. But it regrets this habit once it realizes that it has burned its intended prey to a charred crisp."},{"version":"shield","text":"These Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s bodies are constantly burning. Magmar are feared as one of the causes behind fires."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Legend has it that this Pok\u00e9mon was born from the crater of a volcano. When wounded, it bathes in lava to heal its body, much as one would soak in a hot spring."}],"evo":{"name":"magby","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"magmar","level":1,"min_level":30,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"magmortar","level":2,"min_level":null,"trigger":"trade","item":null,"held_item":"magmarizer","known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/126.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/126.png","capture":45,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":2,"hatch":25,"ev":{"special_attack":2},"forms":[]}